<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #007BFF;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .ip-location {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .ip-location strong {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .reset-link {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .reset-link a {
            color: #007BFF;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .reset-link a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #999999;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
        <div class="ip-location">
            <p><strong>IP Address:</strong>
                <%= ipAddress %>
            </p>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong>
                <%= location.city %>, <%= location.region %>, <%= location.country %>
            </p>
            <p><strong>Time Zone:</strong>
                <%= location.timeZone %>
            </p>
            <p><strong>Coordinates:</strong>
                <%= location.coordinates.join(", ") %></p>
            </div>
        <p>You have requested to reset your password. Please click the link below to proceed with the password reset:
        </p>
        <p class=" reset-link"><a href="<%= resetLink %>">Reset Password</a>
            </p>
            <p>If you did not initiate this password reset or if you believe this request to be suspicious, please
                contact our support team immediately at <a href="mailto:contact@microurl.com"> contact@microurl.com
                </a>. We will be happy to assist you. </p>
            <p>Thank you for your attention to this matter.</p>
            <div class="footer">
                <p>Best regards,<br>microURLs</p>
            </div>
        </div>
</body>

</html>